name: Geoffrey Odlum
body:
### Welcome to my website!
I am a Mechanical Engineering student at Virginia Tech, planning on graduating in May 2018. I have two semesters of co-op experience with the DuPont Company, as well as a summer internship experience with Jacobs Engineering. You can read more about my skills and professional experience in my resume section.
